{"tid":2190004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習「國師」鄭永年被揭性騷擾  遭星洲警嚴厲警告 辭任研究所長","createTime":"2020-09-05T09:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T10:11:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69511d41d45e2fda44fa3207c0f0ecb3ce8c2a83","tid":2190004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/LL3QOCCJZVE6LDCQRC67QLLP3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FLL3QOCCJZVE6LDCQRC67QLLP3I%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=11d08e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FLL3QOCCJZVE6LDCQRC67QLLP3I%2F&h=79eb4f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/LL3QOCCJZVE6LDCQRC67QLLP3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n習「國師」鄭永年被揭性騷擾 <br />\n遭星洲警嚴厲警告 辭任研究所長<br />\n<br />\n【時事追蹤】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：曾參與八九民運 轉軚成左派<br />\n<br />\n獲外界譽為中國國家主席習近平九名「國師」之一的大陸學者鄭永年，近日被指控在擔任新加坡國立大學東亞研究所所長（下稱研究所）期間性騷擾一名女職員。事主曾向大學及研究所投訴，卻被管理層要求息事寧人，這一年以來每日都活在恐懼、絕望之中，如今經過一年掙扎，選擇公開事件。據悉新加坡警方已對鄭發出嚴厲警告，他亦已向大學請辭，本月底離任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mabOLjd9Iwn7bFN61Rb-ylNeTwE=/2208x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASFYBWBT4VF2FFZ7D2KIF7HDS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmabOLjd9Iwn7bFN61Rb-ylNeTwE%3D%2F2208x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASFYBWBT4VF2FFZ7D2KIF7HDS4.jpg&h=dc7b5fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭永年任新加坡國立大學東亞研究所所長，被指在任期間一直性騷擾下屬。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n自稱被鄭永年性騷擾的事主Charlotte，今年8月7日在Twitter發文，披露2018年5月被時任研究所長鄭永年性騷擾，當時正好是她上班的頭一個月。事主指大學和研究所的管理層不但對其。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iiACyjwzcafF1kLIyv7Js1ZlFLA=/1798x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6J6LX5ULT5DQHBPWWMUSEQPRUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiiACyjwzcafF1kLIyv7Js1ZlFLA%3D%2F1798x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6J6LX5ULT5DQHBPWWMUSEQPRUA.jpg&h=b6333082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新加坡國立大學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n校方疑包庇 反迫害事主<br />\n<br />\n事主聲稱自己在研究所還承受不斷的欺凌和攻擊，同時指出鄭永年過去10年在研究所任職的年間，騷擾行為沒有停止，但管理層假裝。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事主在Twitter揭發事件當日另寫道：「每一日，我生活在枯竭、恐懼、絕望之中，感覺自己被困於黑洞。我真的不知如何逃離，可向誰求助。」同時在其twitter標注聯合國婦女署、《華。。。。<br />\n<br />\n東亞研究所前日發聲明表示，留意到社交媒體「針對東亞研究所和它一些在職和前職員的廣泛指摘」的貼文，並指鄭永年已向研究所。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡警方向當地媒體證實，今年4月23日對鄭永年發出有關嚴厲警告。鄭永年今年7月底已經返回內地，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l-0UvgN135Hq47M_hbK9pSnGRrM=/602x702/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/66SG6MBSJ5FEXPNGSWNG2WZJAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl-0UvgN135Hq47M_hbK9pSnGRrM%3D%2F602x702%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F66SG6MBSJ5FEXPNGSWNG2WZJAM.gif&h=de973dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者 / twitter"},{"pid":"94a5c0318c1c619949c7896c780cd3d848c0a043","tid":2190004,"uid":14449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"撚屌國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb08c77190b1c83186d42d3237ae6dca27c6594d","tid":2190004,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee94d0140fcaf7b1a46897868c7e0efc89b4aec","tid":2190004,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F81xV9pY.jpg&amp;h=4d254ca5&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"3dd12a479019e6f86f1904b1537b2dd5b86bd4c3","tid":2190004,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港中文大學（深圳）</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa521a93cb9ab9e355f046523aafa363a9b97915","tid":2190004,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}